{
  "text": "The restricted Laplacian L S is the submatrix of L restricted to S \u00d7 S. And the restricted Green's function G S,\u03b2 is defined as: G S,\u03b2 (\u03b2I S + L S ) = I S , where \u03b2 \u2265 0. Note that L S is positive definite [CITATION_1] , so G S,\u03b2 is well-defined. The PageRank vector pr is defined as:",
